
My personal config for NvChad. 

Installation

    1. Install NvChad base.

       git clone https://github.com/NvChad/starter $env:LOCALAPPDATA\nvim; nvim

    2. Clone my custom config.

       Windows PowerShell:

           git clone https://github.com/wxrayut/nvchad.wxrayut $env:LOCALAPPDATA\nvim; nvim

       Linux/macOS:

           I don't know.

